---
title: Creamy Pesto and Asparagus Orzo with Cheese and Balsamic Drizzle
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Creamy Pesto and Asparagus Orzo in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R21_W48_UK_V17524-2_Main__9low-f86f5ec0.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/65130136723522b64ef4eac8.pdf
author: Lily Stevens
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/creamy-pesto-and-asparagus-orzo-65130136723522b64ef4eac8
time required: 25 minutes
servings: 2
cuisine: Italian
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 900 kcal
  fat: 56.2 g
  saturated fat: 31.1 g
